Text: Succumb to the paralyzing power of fear!
Nowhere to run! Nowhere to hide!
Prepare to witness an ancient Far Eastern ritual!
Do not be shy now. The more the merrier!
It is time for a fight most ferocious: one between man and beast!
Now, watch as my apprentice summons the fearsome Byakko from the folding screen!
Do not fear! We have a noble warrior at hand ready to slay the foul feline.
I can scarce believe my eyes!
Byakko possesses a bulky frame, but he is more agile than most men!
Byakko is more than capable of bewitching any foes that let their guard down.
Byakko is on his last legs! The noble warrior's victory is imminent!
The beast is slain and with that the land has been successfully purified.
This marks the end of our ritual. We do hope you found it to your liking.
Look, the tiger's returned to the folding screen!
Oh dear. It would appear our noble warrior has failed! Byakko has fled to fight another day.
Do not fret. That Byakko was merely an illusion. It cannot sustain its form indefinitely.
A fiercer feline I have never seen.
Are tigers not usually a bit more agile?
Are we certain that's not a real tiger?

<sound(1,51)>An Open tournament is currently in session!
Head to Card Square to sign up and put your Triple Triad talents to the test!
An imitation of...the shikigami of the pyre!
An imitation of...the shikigami of the undertow!
I will erase you from my stage!
This shall be a whirlwind tour!
I never thought I would see this place again.
Right, let's create the mother of all porxies!
I never thought I would see this place again.
We will be counting on your local knowledge.
The facility itself still seems to be in good shape.
What creatures have since taken up residence, I wonder...
So we clear out any pests we encounter, yes?
What creatures have since taken up residence, I wonder...
Whatever they are, we'll make short work of them.
Looks just about as friendly as the rest.
Time to finish tidying up the area.
So that's the keeper of the clay.
Is that supposed to be a golem?
Aye. This is what happens when you neglect to tidy up.
One ingredient struck off the list.
This is fine clay, perfect for our porxie!
If I didn't know better, I would say you were having fun.
So back here again and on to the next task.
A workshop this vast, it certainly makes sense to have portals.
That's right─water to work the clay.
A well-kept area. No doubt thanks to the familiars.
How often did I come here to fetch water for Master Matoya's tea...
That gushing sound... There must be a water vein.
That gushing sound... There must be a water vein.
Correct, and believe me when I say it's icy cold. Watch your step.
What in the world is that thing?
Some manner of sprite? Or another familiar?
That familiar was made with stormwater─and it plays rough. Have care.
As with all things, one cannot judge a familiar by its appearance.
Nothing is so bothersome as a familiar made by an untrained hand.
The water was freezing, but at least it washed the mud away.
Ahhh, to have closure after all these years...
Wait... Was it you who created that familiar!?
Master Matoya will be getting impatient─assuming she hasn't fallen asleep.
Ugh, I'm freezing in my sodden clothes...
Ugh, I'm freezing in my sodden clothes...
Worry not, you will be warm again soon. Very warm.
Good heavens, is the magma rainbow-colored? Spectacular!
Ungh, the aether here is so vivid, I can scarcely see...
These colors... I take it the magma is infused with the elements.
Good heavens, is the magma rainbow-colored? Spectacular!
The product of dissolved crystals, lest you wonder.
And now the kiln should be lit!
Whew, I shall be glad to leave this stifling place behind.
Such an aether-rich heat source will be perfect for porxie-making.
And now the kiln should be lit!
Aye, let us return to Master Matoya.
So for the finishing touches, we employ...brute force?
A pugnacious specimen...just like its creator.
Garb aside, I suspect the creature will be anything but regal.
They can come from anywhere. Stay alert.
Ahhh! My head! The pain, the pain!
Indeed. Without your magicks, we would be done for.
Everyone back! I will shield Alisaie!
Don't get distracted. Focus on the mission.
We should be able to move it using this panel.
I'm not picking up any more hostiles.
Still not enjoying the creepy voice, thanks!
Well, you know what to do!
There's no choice. We do it.
Gather as many eggs as you can!
Fools you were to come here!
Now you face the raging storm, netherlings!
You cannot hope to defeat us!
Hold still! These ones will heal friendly fighting ones!
This is as far as you go!
You'll have to do better than that!
Have faith and victory shall be ours.
I do not like the look of that...
Well, let us see how its defenses fare against this!
By the gods... Is that the Allagan relic!?
Come, my children. There is work to be done!
Their flames will sear the flesh from your bones!
Rise from the ashes, and lay waste to our enemies!
The flames will consume you all!
Time is mine to command. Mine to control!
Is there no end to them!?
Sun, sea, and sandy beaches─there's no place like the Isle of Endless Summer!
Hey! Take it easy, will you?
Did they just wash up on shore?
Is it just me, or is there a chill in the air?
A chill? It's downright freezing! Brrrrrr...
Let's get out of here before we freeze to death!

Adjusting tactic protocols...
Enhancing right arm.

Adjusting tactic protocols...
Enhancing left arm.
No way forward, no way back!

You would grant me succor?
Are you not our enemy?

Thank you, overdweller!
Let me show you the way!
May you finally be at peace.
The combined might of both dragon and dragoon...

Lord Aymeric!
Let me take care of this!

We shall see the wounded to safety.
You are needed elsewhere!
That should give us a moment's rest.

Help is on the way.
Please, hold on a little longer...

Stand firm!
We cannot afford to lose!

There is nowhere left to run, Yamatsumi!
Give yourself into our custody!
We sympathize with your plight, but we will not allow you to subject Bozja to your depravations!

Spare me your pity!
We are foes─I accept naught from you but pain and blood!
Pride of our line, greatest of the shikigami, I summon thee forth!

Slay them, yoki!
Smear their offal upon the rocks!

Bah, you try my patience!
Protect me, shikigami! I command it!
Is this where our line ends?

It cannot be!
Yoki is broken!?
The greatest shikigami we have ever commanded... Fallen.
Come, Yamatsumi! We shall have another chance at revenge!

Your quiver of tricks is empty, Yamatsumi.
Now surrender!

Surrender?
The Urabe will return, stronger than before!
Hehe... The relic bends to my will. As is to be expected from one with my talents.
I am master of man and artifact alike, and finally the stage for my masterpiece is set! Haha!
Where are the advance forces? I see no sign of them.
What was that, Kosyu? These are the selfsame fiends Lady Fran reported sighting in Dalmasca? It can't be!
Now do you see!? My art is beyond challenge!
We will yet prevail, Master Oboro!
Your task is to make stuffed toys using the materials laid out on the Mattock, kupo.
Once you've finished sewing together a toy, take it to a wain at the central plaza.
Make lots of stuffed toys and deliver them all, kupo!
We hope you enjoyed that veritable parade of oversized stuffed toys. The next fête is “Shear-a-Yak,” and it will be held at Bright Ballad's Passage!
Though you'll be shearing a yak in this fête, instead of shears, you'll be using an enhanced version of the aetheromatic auger: the aetheromatic clipper!
Tuned to operate with normal concentrations of aether, it shoots blasts of magicked wind that effortlessly removes fleece from their owners!
So get firing at the yak, and bring the fleece it sheds to me, three sacks full at a time!
That's all for “Shear-a-Yak.” Now, please take yourselves to the Abacus for the next fête: “Toy Hunter”!
My swinelings have hidden a lucky toy in one of three present boxes.
You must open the right box to find the toy, and then bring it to me.
Great hunting, everyone. Now, please make your way to the central plaza on the Mattock!
I bid you welcome to the final fête: “Presents of Mind”!
In this fête, you must deliver presents to various folk on the Mattock according to the mascots' instructions.
Upon delivering two presents, the mascot issuing the instructions will change, so be sure to pay attention. Let the gifting begin!
It's farewell for now, but we look forward to seeing you again! Till next time!
Nothing up my sleeves─save my muscular arms─and presto! We have materials!
Just a moment while we prepare.
Hm, perhaps I need a speech quirk like “kupo” as well...
Wind direction─check. Wind speed─check. Everything is in order!
Thank you for your patience! The fête will now begin!
Heh heh, our wooly friend looks like a new yak!
Now it's time for me and my swinelings to get to work!
My massive muscles will make short work of the tidying up.
It's time to hide the toy.
Speech quirks are for the weak...kupo.
This is it, everyone─the final fête.
We mascots are all taking part this time.
Have fun with us till the end!
The final fête is upon us. Are you ready, my dear mascots?
Let us finish on a high note!
We hope you had as much fun as we did!
Looks like this goes all the way up.
Hear ye, hear ye! Fêtes are about to commence!
Greetings, friends, and thank you for joining in the Skyrise Celebration!
Today, we will be hosting a variety of fêtes─the first of which serves as an introduction to our friendly team of mascots.
Mighty Moogle, at your service, kupo. Made of sterner stuff though I am, I'm in charge of the fête “Made of Softer Stuff”!
Chirpy Chocobo is my name, and “Shear-a-Yak” is my game. Under my fluffy wing, you will shear as you've never shorn before!
And last but definitely not least, I am Perky Piggy. My swinelings and I look forward to making a “Toy Hunter” out of you!
Remember these mascots well, for they will be your guides throughout the revelry. On which note, let us dive into the fête!
The mascots will take turns striking their favorite poses, and we ask that you show your celebratory spirit by posing in kind.
Here is a pose that maximizes your muscular appeal.
Do the mighty maximizer, and show the fine specimen that you are, kupo!
Before using the aetheromatic clipper, it is important to point and acknowledge.
To that end, we do the chirpy checker!
When searching for treasure, one must keep one's eyes peeled.
To help you practice, I bid you do the perky peeler with me!
Hereon, the order will be random.
Before using the aetheromatic clipper, point and acknowledge with the chirpy checker!
When searching for treasure, keep your eyes peeled with the perky peeler!
Show the fine specimen that you are with the mighty maximizer, kupo!
I trust you are now acquainted with our friendly mascots. With that, let us move right along to the next fête.
Mighty Moogle, whose big muscles are equaled only by his big heart, awaits you on the Mattock for “Made of Softer Stuff”!
I am Pagaga, beastmaster of the proud line of Vochstein!
Are there any out there with stones enough to face me and my pets!?
...You lot? Ahahaha! I was expecting something a little sterner, but very well! Let's see how you fare!
Come, Berda! Obda! I've found you some playmates!
Away, Obda! I won't have you dying on me!
To think that my prized beasts could be bested...
Grrr... We'll get you next time! Mark my words!
Hmph, this the best the Resistance's got? Lyon's fallen far to struggle against your ilk.
What? These monsters were once your allies!?
They were once, but they are far past saving. He says killing them would be a mercy. I'm of the same mind, Kosyu─let's end this, and quickly.
Impudent rebels. You are hardly worthy to lay eyes upon my masterwork. Grovel for the chance I've afforded you!
Now, my puppets, dance and leave the world agog with your grace!
O, earth beneath me, heed my call! Rise up and crush these Resistance vermin into so much dust!
It is time to show what you can do, my minion. Go forth and crush the Resistance underfoot!
Hmph, we'll shatter it like the ice it is!
We need waste no more time on this rabble.
Let us save our strength for the next mission.
Owww, that hurts! Seriously, <split(<String>ObjectParameter(1)</String>, ,1)>, you're a <If(PlayerParameter(4))>woman<Else/>man</If> after my own heart!
\\<pant> Bugger me, where did my strength go...?
Fight harder, you lot! Fight harder!
We must free them! Target the constricting flames!
Resistance scum. Finally, you show yourselves...
Come, my new and improved Dabog! Show these fools the power of Delta Gabriel Kai!
It is Dabog inside that golden machina? Gods have mercy...
This is hyperpilot Dabog. Target confirmed. Commencing combat operations...
This is hyperpilot Dabog. Hull damage...confirmed. Firepower...below acceptable parameters.
Deploying long-range assault nodes... Initiating omnidirectional attack...
This is hyperpilot Dabog. Hull integrity...compromised. Proceeding with combat operations...
You would do well not to underestimate us!
Such firepower! Retreat, I say... Retreat!
From the savior's own hands... Such an honor this is!
\\<gasp> These are the latest tools! However did you know?

What might this be?
...Oho, new masonry tools!
Thank you! I will treasure this!
Ooh, birch syrup, and quality stuff to boot!
Heh heh, I shall enjoy this with my tea!
